title: [Smuggling Tunnels, Passage]
description: Although the air is still, you would swear you heard the whisper of wind.  A single coin of unrecognizable origin sits forgotten in the dirt next to one wall, the owner long since gone from this place.  Even the token-loving rats have left it be, for not even tiny footprints walk around it.
paths: Obvious exits: north, east, southwest, northwest
